msgstr "允許在 localhost 本地主機上，進行 tcp 連線"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:98
msgid "Allow tcp connection from 192.168.1.x network"
msgstr "允許由 192.168.1.x 網絡提出的 tcp 連線"

